answers.answer: I'm sure you'll do fine Mommy! Just take it easy & I'm sure you have everything ready its just a Mommy thing worrying.
I Had PreEclampsia With Both Of My Kids... Mine Was So Bad That They Induced Me Asap. 36 Weeks With My Son 38 With My Daughter. But Im Sure You Will Be Fine! :) Good Luck.

title: excited and scared
